No. 43,

Mise.

Banks v. California. Thomas C. Lynch, Attorney General of California, Albert W. Harris, Jr., Assistant Attorney General, and Louise H. Renne, Deputy Attorney General, for respondent.

Ct. App. Cal., 1st App. Dist. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Certiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
